	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You crack two raw eggs into each other, mingling their insides, and as you do so the minds of nearby creatures psychically link.</em></p><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 1 Minute</p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><ul><li><p>Each target is telepathically connected to all the others and can at any time choose to telepathically communicate to them all simultaneously via thought.</p></li><li><p>Communication is possible over any distance, but cannot extend to other planes.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><em>Creatures that do not share a language cannot understand each other telepathically. A spell such as @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.yJzrgvxa2QVSAr6z]{Tongues} or @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.K9TCdZs4SV9PqI2i]{Speak with Animals} can allow you to telepathically communicate with creatures you cannot typically understand.</em></p>",
